Ensure every scene has a valid image_prompt.
- For speaker "A"/"B" scenes: include character tags in image_prompt.
- For "Narrator" scenes: these are background/environment shots with NO human character. Use only scenery, atmosphere, and object tags (e.g. `scenery`, `no_humans`, `outdoors`, `building`).
